    "body": "On the [solidity side](https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/992) we will soon distinguish between functions that do not modify state but can read state and actual pure functions which only depend on their arguments (and not on the state).\n\nAdding `PURE_CALL` can enforce that on EVM-level and would also allow some optimizations at execution time.\n",
